### GroupCoordinator response error: Broker: Group coordinator not available

Occurs when using RdKafka\KafkaConsumer with Kafka < 0.9, or Kafka has not
finished booting.

### Local: Invalid argument or configuration

You are using offset.store.method=broker (default in librdkafka 0.9) without
having set a group id. Try setting the group.id configuration property, or
setting offset.store.method to 'file'.

